data.title: POP 1: Todd Woodbridge RC BGS 9.5: 1993 NetPro Tour Stars Rookie Card Gisto
data.meta_description: GISTO or Gisto stands for “Graded 1 st Overall”. Stylized as G1STO. This Card is the Gisto and a POP 1. What is a GISTO?. It’s the first card that is graded for each card that is released. Whether it’s 1st edition books, 1 st edition Pokémon cards, 1st Off-the-line Sports Cars, or the 1 st in a print run for serial numbers on cards getting the 1 st is always the most important.
